        </p>
        <p>Beneficiary Name
          <input type="text" placeholder="Jungggle Inc.">        
        </p>
        <p>Baneficiary Address
          <input type="text" placeholder="401 Seodo-building 1712-8 Seocho-dong Seocho-gu, Korea">
        </p>
        <p>Bank Name
          <input type="text" placeholder="INDUSTRIAL BANK OF KOREA">
        </p>
        <p>Bank Address
          <input type="text" placeholder="50 ULCHIRO 2-GA, CHUNG-GU Seoul, Korea">
        </p>
        <h5>Your Cash Out fee is : $0<br>for more terms, please check it in <a href="#none">here.</a></h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn" data-toggle="modal" data-dismiss="modal" data-target="#Modal-add-credit">Cash Out</button>
